  "title": "Sports Coaching",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Duties and\nResponsibilities:</strong></u><u> </u></p><p>·       \nPlan and deliver\nstructured coaching sessions appropriate to participants’ age and ability\nlevels</p><p>·       \nTeach correct\ntechniques, rules, and strategies for swimming and sailing</p><p>·       \nSupport athlete\ndevelopment from beginner to advanced levels</p><p>·       \nMonitor individual\nprogress and provide constructive feedback</p><p>·       \nEnsure all sessions\ncomply with health, safety, and safeguarding policies</p><p>·       \nMaintain constant\nsupervision during water-based activities</p><p>·       \nConduct risk\nassessments and ensure safe use of equipment and facilities</p><p>·       \nRespond appropriately\nto emergencies, following established procedures</p><p><u><strong>Programme Development</strong></u></p><p>·       \nAssist in developing\ntraining programmes, lesson plans, and seasonal schedules</p><p>·       \nSupport competitions,\nregattas, swim meets, and events where required</p><p>·       \nEncourage\nparticipation, motivation, and positive sporting values</p><p><u><strong>Required Qualifications\n& Experience</strong></u></p><p>·       \nRecognized coaching\nqualification in Swimming and/or Sailing</p><p>·       \nFirst Aid and CPR\ncertification</p><p>·       \nProven experience\ncoaching swimming and/or sailing</p><p>·       \nStrong knowledge of\nwater safety and safeguarding practices</p>",
