    "description": "<p>Little Splashes Swim School conducts swimming lessons for infants from 6 months old and above. Our programs are created to build water confidence, water safety and survival skills.</p>\n\n<p>Lesson duration is 30 minutes for all levels. Student ratio is kept small to focus and customized according to individual’s learning ability.</p>\n\n<p>Our facility is based in Siglap Community Centre. Our pool is an indoor heated with mineral water.</p>\n",
